text: The 1944 Idaho gubernatorial election was held on November 7, 1944. Democratic nominee Charles C. Gossett defeated Republican nominee W. H. Detweiler with 52.64% of the vote. ==General election== ===Candidates=== *Charles C. Gossett, Democratic *W. H. Detweiler, Republican ===Results=== ==References== 1944 Idaho Gubernatorial
title: 1944 Idaho gubernatorial election
